data.col_0: Required Response Date and Time: March 21, 2025, no later than 10am PDT
Do not change the template formatting. Columns P through AB should include numbers only. If there are any other characters in these fields  it will be considered a no bid.
Rates must be provided in USD .
Please include a 10% Volume Incentive in your response.
ATA and ATD rates should include all terminal handling fees.
DTD rates should include pick up within a 80km radius with the exception of HKG which should include Hong Kong, New Territories and Kowloon Island.
Transit days: Express 3-4 business days & Deferred 5-7 days business days.
All rates and charges including fuel and security must be fixed from May 1, 2025 and April 30, 2026.
Fuel and Security must be separate charges. We will not accept "all in" rates.
NO additional surcharges will be applicable to any quoted or published rates starting on May 1, 2025.
Payment terms are Net 75 days from invoice date of receipt.
Forwarder is responsible for full value of any loss or damage up to $50,000 USD per HAWB.
All lanes must be completed we will not accept partial bids.

The information contained within this document and all other documents associated with this RFP are confidential .  Without the express written consent of the Sanmina Corp, no party shall disclose the terms, information or data contained this document or any information obtained as a result of participating in this Request for Proposal.  All data and information provided or used in connection with this Request for Proposal is and shall remain the exclusive property of Sanmina Corp.
